OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few light showers around at
OL,6,Ffirst. Otherwise a dry day with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing from late afternoon with
OL,9,Fpatchy rain into the Isles and west
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain in the west will soon
OL,13,Fspread to all parts through the
OL,14,Fevening, becoming heavy for a time
OL,15,Fbefore clearing before dawn, followed
OL,16,Fby clear spells and blustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
