OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FBright spells and blustery
OL,6,Fshowers at first. Drier for a time in
OL,7,Fthe middle of the day before further
OL,8,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,9,Fand blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,12,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday with
OL,13,Fscattered heavy showers, the showers
OL,14,Fdying out through Thursday evening.
OL,15,FChance of overnight frosts. Mostly dry
OL,16,Fon Friday, some rain far northwest
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
